          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-1" n="1">To Fair Lady Betty Dan: Sat for his Picture,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-2" n="2">And Defy'd Her to Draw him so oft that he Piqu'd her</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-3" n="3">He knew She'd no Pencil or Colouring by her;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-4" n="4">And therefore he thought he might safely defy her.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-5" n="5">Come Sit says my Lady then whips up her Scissars</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-6" n="6">And Cuts out his Coxcomb in silk in a Trice sirs:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-7" n="7">Dan: sat with Attention, and saw with surprise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-8" n="8">How She Lengthen'd his Chin, how she hollow'd his Eyes;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-9" n="9">And Flatter'd himself with a secret conceit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-10" n="10">That his Leathern Jaws all her Art would defeat.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-11" n="11">Lady Betty observ'd it, then pulls out a Pin</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-12" n="12">And Varies the Grain of the stuff to his Chin.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-13" n="13">And to make roasted silk resemble his Raw bone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-14" n="14">She rais'd up a Thread to the Jett of his Jaw bone;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-15" n="15">'Till at length in Exactest proportion he rose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-16" n="16">From the Crown of his head to the Arch of his Nose.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-17" n="17">And if Lady Betty had Drawn him with Wigg &amp; all</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-18" n="18">'Tis certain the Coppy had out done the Original</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-19" n="19">Well that's but my Outside, says Dan: with a Vapour</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-20" n="20">Say You so says my Lady, I've Lin'd it with Paper</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-991A002D-line-21" n="21">«LD»Patt: Delany sculpsit.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
